1. Clone both repos into the same parent folder so they sit side by side:

  capstone/
    local_host_pipeline/
    grafana_custom_plugin/

2. In grafana_custom_plugin, install dependencies and build the plugin:

  npm install
  npm run build

3. In local_host_pipeline, start the full pipeline:

  docker compose up

4. In local_host_pipeline/smart_metrics, install dependencies and start the API:

  npm install
  npm start

5. In sample_app (sibling directory to the others in my strucutre, could be anywhere), start the metrics generator:

  npm install
  npm run dev

6. Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser. Log in with admin / admin. The Trickl plugin should be accessible from the left nav. It might take a minute
or two for recs to start hitting. Be warned, the bike is operational, so the YAML file will be updated everything you hit submit!